# Ship classes of Imperial Grand Fleet
#
# Number 1xx, 2xx, 3xx, ..., 500 -> Tech level
# x00, 10, 20, ... -> Ship size - 1
# ex) 490 class is ship size 10, TL 4 ship
#
# Class name is temporary just the number
# 
# key is class number +9000
#
# 2000/3/20, outsider

